(15, 'inline_html', '<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp;&nbsp;For survival and proliferation the organism has to grow , defend against adverse conditions, infectious diseases etc., and to perform all these processes energy is required.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; Plants convert light energy into chemical energy which will be used for the synthesis of several substances required for growth and survival.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp;Glucose and fatty acids are the major sunbstances used for energy production in all the organisms.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; Oxidation of food materials , especially glucose, fatty acids and proteins to carbon dioxide and water is called Respiration. Energy is produced in this process.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; As this process occurs at cellular level called Cellular respiration.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; Energy produced in this proces is used by the cells to carry out several acitivities such as synthesis of molecules, transport of ions and nutrients etc..</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', 'Respiration is an essential process', 'Respiration is a life process in the organism', '<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp;&nbsp;For survival and proliferation the organism has to grow , defend against adverse conditions, infectious diseases etc., and to perform all these processes energy is required.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; Plants convert light energy into chemical energy which will be used for the synthesis of several substances required for growth and survival.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp;Glucose and fatty acids are the major sunbstances used for energy production in all the organisms.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; Oxidation of food materials , especially glucose, fatty acids and proteins to carbon dioxide and water is called Respiration. Energy is produced in this process.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; As this process occurs at cellular level called Cellular respiration.</p>\n\n<p>$ \\bigstar $ &nbsp; Energy produced in this proces is used by the cell