nbsp;= &nbsp;displacement &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;body</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; a &nbsp;= &nbsp;uniform &nbsp;acceleration</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>( 1 ) : &nbsp; &nbsp; v &nbsp;= &nbsp;u &nbsp;+ &nbsp;at</p>\n\n<p>Acceleration &nbsp; is &nbsp;rate &nbsp; of &nbsp;change &nbsp;of &nbsp;velocity</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; a &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{v &nbsp;- &nbsp;u}{t} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;at &nbsp;= &nbsp;v &nbsp;- &nbsp;u</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;v &nbsp;= &nbsp;u &nbsp;+ &nbsp;at</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>( 2 ) : &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;s &nbsp;= &nbsp;ut &nbsp;+ &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ &nbsp;a $ t^{2} $ &nbsp; &nbsp;.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Average &nbsp; velocity &nbsp; of &nbsp;a &nbsp;body &nbsp;moving &nbsp;with &nbsp;uniform &nbsp;acceleration &nbsp;is &nbsp;given &nbsp;by</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;v &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{u&nbsp; + &nbsp;v}{2} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;The &nbsp;distance &nbsp;travelled &nbsp;by &nbsp;the &nbsp;body &nbsp;in &nbsp;time &nbsp;&#39;t&#39; &nbsp;is</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;s &nbsp;= &nbsp;average &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;X &nbsp; time</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{u&nbsp; + &nbsp;v}{2} $ &nbsp; x &nbsp; t</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; but &nbsp;v &nbsp; = &nbsp;u &nbsp;+ &nbsp;at</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; s &nbsp;= &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{u&nbsp; + [u &nbsp;+ &nbsp;at]&nbsp;}{2} $ &nbsp; x &nbsp;t</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; s &nbsp;= &nbsp; &nbsp;$ \\frac{ut &nbsp;+ ut &nbsp;+ &nbsp;at^{2}&nbsp;}{2} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;s &nbsp;= &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{&nbsp;2ut &nbsp;+ &nbsp;at^{2}&nbsp;}{2} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;s &nbsp; = &nbsp;ut &nbsp;+ &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ &nbsp;a&nbsp;$ t^{2} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>( 3 ) : &nbsp;$ v^{2} $ &nbsp;- &nbsp;$ u^{2} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp; 2as</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; we &nbsp;have &nbsp;seen &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; s &nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{u&nbsp; + &nbsp;v}{2} $ &nbsp; x &nbsp; t</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;From &nbsp;this</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; u &nbsp;+ &nbsp;v &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{2s}{t} $ ---------------------- (a)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Also &nbsp; v &nbsp; = &nbsp;u &nbsp;+ &nbsp;at</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;v &nbsp;- &nbsp;u &nbsp; = &nbsp;at &nbsp;-------------------(b)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Multiplying &nbsp;(a) &nbsp; and &nbsp; (b)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; (v &nbsp;+ &nbsp;u) &nbsp;(v &nbsp;-&nbsp; u) &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{2s}{t} $ &nbsp; X &nbsp;at</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;$ v^{2} $ &nbsp;- &nbsp;$ u^{2} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp; 2as</p>\n', 0, 0);
