(4424, '<p>If m and n are &nbsp;positive &nbsp;integers, &nbsp;then &nbsp;for &nbsp;a positive &nbsp;number x, &nbsp;[$ &nbsp;\\sqrt[m]{&nbsp;\\sqrt[n]{x} &nbsp;} &nbsp;^{mn} $] is .............</p>\n', '<p>$ ( \\sqrt[m]{&nbsp;\\sqrt[n]{x} &nbsp;})&nbsp; ^{mn} $&nbsp; = $ ( \\sqrt[m]{ &nbsp;x^{\\frac{1}{n}}&nbsp;} ) ^{mn} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; =&nbsp;&nbsp;$ [&nbsp;&nbsp;(x^{\\frac{1}{n}})^{&nbsp;\\frac{1}{m}&nbsp;}]^{mn}&nbsp;$ =&nbsp;$ (&nbsp;x^{&nbsp;\\frac{1}{mn}&nbsp;}&nbsp;)^{mn} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;=&nbsp;$ x^{1} $ = &nbsp;$x$&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Ans : &nbsp;A</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4425, '<p>If&nbsp;$ [64^{x}&nbsp;$] =&nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{&nbsp;256^{y} &nbsp;} $ = 2$ \\sqrt{2} $, &nbsp;then &nbsp;3x+4y is ...........</p>\n', '<p>&nbsp;$ (64)^{x}&nbsp;$&nbsp;=&nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{ (256)^{y} &nbsp;} $ = 2$ \\sqrt{2} $</p>\n\n<p>$ (64)^{x}&nbsp;$&nbsp; = &nbsp;2$ \\sqrt{2} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;$ (&nbsp;2^{6} &nbsp;)^{x}&nbsp;$ = &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$ (2)^{1+&nbsp;\\frac{1}{2} &nbsp;}&nbsp;$</p>\n\n<p>$ (2)^{6x}&nbsp;$ =&nbsp;$ (2)^{\\frac{3}{2}&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;$</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;6$x$ &nbsp;= $&nbsp;{\\frac{3}{2}&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;$&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>$x$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;$&nbsp;{\\frac{1}{4}&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;$&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{ (256)^{y} &nbsp;} $ = 2$ \\sqrt{2} $</p>\n\n<p>$ (256)^{-y} $ &nbsp;=&nbsp;&nbsp;2$ \\sqrt{2} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;$ (&nbsp;2^{8})^{-y}&nbsp;$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ (2)^{\\frac{3}{2}&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;$</p>\n\n<p>$ 2^{-8y}&nbsp;$ =&nbsp;$ 2^{\\frac{3}{2}&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;$</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;- 8y &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{3}{2} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; y&nbsp; =&nbsp;$ \\frac{-3}{16} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>3x + 4y &nbsp;= &nbsp;3 ($ \\frac{1}{4} $) + 4 ($ \\frac{-3}{16} $ )&nbsp;=&nbsp;$ \\frac{3}{4} $ -&nbsp;$ \\frac{3}{4} $ = 0</p>\n\n<p>Ans : B</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
