(4495, '<p>The &nbsp;coefficient &nbsp;of &nbsp;$ x^{3} $ in 3$ x^{4} $-5$ x^{2} $+7 is</p>\n', '<p>3$ x^{4} $-5$ x^{2} $+7 =&nbsp;3$ x^{4} $ +&nbsp;$ x^{3}(0) $- 5$ x^{2} $ + &nbsp;x(0) +7</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; coefficient &nbsp;of &nbsp; $ x^{3}$ &nbsp;= 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; Ans : A</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4496, '<p>Find &nbsp;the &nbsp;value &nbsp;of &nbsp;polynomial &nbsp; 4$ x^{2} $-5x+3 &nbsp; when &nbsp;x = $ \\frac{1}{2} $</p>\n', '<p>4$ x^{2} $- &nbsp;5x &nbsp;+ 3 =&nbsp;4$ (&nbsp;\\frac{1}{2})&nbsp;^{2} $- 5($ \\frac{1}{2})$&nbsp;+ 3</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 4 $ (&nbsp;\\frac{1}{4})&nbsp;&nbsp;$ -&nbsp;($ \\frac{5}{2})$ + 3</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 4 -&nbsp;($ \\frac{5}{2})$ &nbsp;=&nbsp;$ \\frac{3}{2}$</p>\n\n<p>Ans : D</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4497, '<p>find &nbsp;p(-2) &nbsp;for &nbsp;the &nbsp;polynomial &nbsp;p(y)=2 + y + 2$ y^{2} $- $ y^{3} $</p>\n', '<p>p(y) =2 + y + 2$ y^{2} $- $ y^{3} $</p>\n\n<p>p(-2) = 2 + (-2) + 2$ (-2)^{2} $ - $ (-2)^{3} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= 2 - 2 + 2 ( 4 ) - ( - 8) &nbsp;= 8 +&nbsp;8 = 16</p>\n\n<p>Ans : A</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4498, '<p>What &nbsp;is &nbsp;the &nbsp;zero &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;polynomial &nbsp;f(x) = px, &nbsp;p &nbsp;$ \\neq&nbsp;$ &nbsp;0 &nbsp;is&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>px &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;x &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{0}{p} $ &nbsp;= 0</p>\n\n<p>Ans : B</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4499, '<p>If &nbsp;0 &nbsp;and &nbsp;1 &nbsp;are &nbsp;the &nbsp;zeros &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;polynomial &nbsp;f(x) = 2$ x^{3} $ - 3$ x^{2} $ + ax + b , then (a , b)=.........</p>\n', '<p>f (0) = 0 ,&nbsp;f (x) = 2$ x^{3} $ - 3$ x^{2} $ + ax + b</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;f (0) =&nbsp;&nbsp;2$ (0)^{3} $ - 3$ (0)^{2} $ + a(0)&nbsp;+ b</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; 0 &nbsp;= 0 - 0 + 0 + b&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>b = 0</p>\n\n<p>and&nbsp;f (1) = 0</p>\n\n<p>2$&nbsp;(1)^{3} $ - 3$&nbsp;(1)^{2} $ + a(1)&nbsp;+ b = 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;2 - 3 + a + b = 0</p>\n\n<p>- 1 + a + 0 = 0</p>\n\n<p>a = 1</p>\n\n<p>( a , b ) &nbsp;=&nbsp;( 1&nbsp;, 0&nbsp;)</p>\n\n<p>Ans : C</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4500, '<p>The &nbsp;remainder &nbsp;when $ x^{3} $+3$ x^{2} $+3x+1 &nbsp;is &nbsp;divided &nbsp;by &nbsp;5 + 2x</p>\n', '<p>&nbsp;f (x) = $ x^{3} $+3$ x^{2} $+3x+1 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5 + 2x = 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;The &nbsp;remainder &nbsp;= &nbsp;f ( -&nbsp;$ \\frac{5}{2} $ ) &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;x =&nbsp;&nbsp;-&nbsp;$ \\frac{5}{2} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;f (-&nbsp;$ \\frac{5}{2} $&nbsp;) = $ (-\\frac{5}{2} )^{3} $+3$ (-\\frac{5}{2} )^{2} $+3(-$\\frac{5}{2}$ )+1 &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;$ \\frac{-125}{8} $ &nbsp; +&nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{75}{4} $ &nbsp;- &nbsp;$ \\frac{15}{2} $ + 1</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{-125 &nbsp;+ &nbsp;150 &nbsp;- &nbsp;60 &nbsp;+ &nbsp;8}{8} $&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; =&nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{-27}{8} $&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Ans : C</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4501, '<p>If &nbsp;(x-2) is &nbsp;exactly &nbsp;dividing &nbsp;both &nbsp;the &nbsp;expressions 2$ x^{3} $ + k$ x^{2} $ + 3x - 5 and&nbsp;&nbsp;$ x^{3} $ + $ x^{2} $ - 4x + k &nbsp;then</p>\n', '<p>Let &nbsp;f (x) &nbsp;= &nbsp;2$ x^{3} $+k$ x^{2} $+3x-5 &nbsp;and&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;g&nbsp;(x) &nbsp; = &nbsp;$ x^{3} $+$ x^{2} $- 4x + k&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;given &nbsp;that&nbsp;&nbsp;f (2) &nbsp;= &nbsp;g&nbsp;(2)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;2$ (2)^{3} $+k$ (2)^{2} $ + 3(2)&nbsp;- 5 &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ (2)^{3} $ + $ (2)^{2} $ - 4(2)&nbsp;+ k</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 16 + k (4) + 6 - 5 = 8 + 4 - 8 + k</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4k +&nbsp;17 &nbsp;= &nbsp;k &nbsp;+ 4</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4k - k &nbsp;= &nbsp;4 - 17&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3k &nbsp;= &nbsp;-13</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;k = &nbsp;$ \\frac{-13}{3} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ans : &nbsp;D</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4502, '<p>If &nbsp;($ x^{2} $-1) &nbsp;is &nbsp;a &nbsp;factor &nbsp;of &nbsp; a$ x^{4} $ + b$ x^{3} $ + &nbsp;c$ x^{2} $ + dx + e then&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>Let &nbsp;f (x) &nbsp;= &nbsp;a$ x^{4} $+ b$ x^{3} $+ c$ x^{2} $ + dx + e</p>\n\n<p>($ x^{2} $-1) is &nbsp;a &nbsp;factor &nbsp;of &nbsp;&nbsp;f (x)</p>\n\n<p>$ x^{2} $-1 &nbsp;= &nbsp;(x - 1)&nbsp;(x +&nbsp;1)&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>According &nbsp;to &nbsp;the &nbsp;sum &nbsp;&nbsp;f (1) = 0 and&nbsp;&nbsp;f (-1) = 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; f (1) &nbsp;=&nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;a$ (1)^{4} $ + &nbsp;b$ (1)^{3} $ + c$ (1)^{2} $ + d(1)&nbsp;+ e &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; a + b + c + d + e = 0 &nbsp;--------------(1)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;f (-1) &nbsp;=&nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;a$&nbsp;(-1)^{4} $+ b$&nbsp;(-1)^{3} $+ c$&nbsp;(-1)^{2} $ + d(-1)&nbsp;+ e &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>a -&nbsp;b + c -&nbsp;d + e = 0&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>a &nbsp;+ c&nbsp;+ e &nbsp;= &nbsp;b &nbsp;+ d</p>\n\n<p>Substitute &nbsp;this &nbsp;value &nbsp;in &nbsp;eqn &nbsp;(1)</p>\n\n<p>a + b + c + d + e = 0</p>\n\n<p>b + d + b + d = 0</p>\n\n<p>2(b + d) = 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;b + d = 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; a + c + e &nbsp;=&nbsp; b + d &nbsp;= 0</p>\n\n<p>Ans : B</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4503, '<p>Factorise &nbsp; $ x^{3} $ - 2&nbsp;$ x^{2} $ - x + 2</p>\n', '<p>Let f(x) =&nbsp;$ x^{3} $ - 2$ x^{2} $ - x + 2</p>\n\n<p>by trial f(1) =&nbsp;$ 1^{3} $ - 2($ 1^{2} $ - (1) + 2 = 0</p>\n\n<p>Therefore (x-1) is a factor of f(x)</p>\n\n<p>$ \\frac{(x-1)}{(x^{3} &nbsp;- 2&nbsp;x^{2} - x + 2)&nbsp;&nbsp;} $ = $ x^{2} $ &nbsp;- x - 2</p>\n\n<p>Therefore f(x) = (x-1)($ x^{2} $ - x -2)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; =(x-1)[($ x^{2} $-2x+x-2)]&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; =(x-1)[x(x-2) +(x-2)]</p>\n\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; =(x-1)(x-2)(x+1)</span></p>\n\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">Ans : A&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.6em;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4504, '<p>If &nbsp;a$ x^{2} $ + bx + c &nbsp;and &nbsp;b$ x^{2} $ + ax + c &nbsp;have &nbsp;a &nbsp;common &nbsp;factor &nbsp;(x+1) &nbsp;then&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>&nbsp;Let &nbsp;f (x) &nbsp;= &nbsp;a$ x^{2} $ + bx + c and&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;g&nbsp;(x) &nbsp;= &nbsp;b$ x^{2} $ + ax + c&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Given that&nbsp;f (-1) &nbsp; = &nbsp;g&nbsp;(-1)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;a$ (-1)^{2} $ + b(-1)&nbsp;+ c &nbsp;= &nbsp;b$ (-1)^{2} $ + a(-1)&nbsp;+ c</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; a &nbsp;- &nbsp;b = b - &nbsp;a</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 2a = 2b</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;a = b</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;f (-1) &nbsp;= &nbsp;a - b + c = 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;b&nbsp;- b + c &nbsp;= 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; c = &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; Ans : D</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
