(4506, '<p>If (y - 3) &nbsp;is &nbsp;a &nbsp;factor &nbsp;of &nbsp;$ y^{3} $ - 2$ y^{2} $ - 9y -18 , then &nbsp;the &nbsp;other &nbsp;two &nbsp;factors&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>Let f(y) =&nbsp;$ y^{3} $ - 2$ y^{2} $ - 9(y) - 18</p>\n\n<p>Given that (y-3) is a factor of f(y)</p>\n\n<p>$ \\frac{(y-3)}{(&nbsp;y^{3}- 2&nbsp;y^{2} - 9y +18)&nbsp;&nbsp;} $</p>\n\n<p>=(y-3)($ y^{2} $ + y - 6)</p>\n\n<p>Therefore f(y) = (y-3)($ y^{2} $ + y - 6)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;=(y-3)[$ y^{2} $+ 3y - 2y - 6]</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;=(y-3)[(y(y+3) - 2(y+3)]</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;=(y-3)(y+3)(y-2)</p>\n\n<p>Therefore the other two factors are (y-2) and (y+3)</p>\n\n<p>Ans : C</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4507, '<p>$ (&nbsp;&nbsp;\\frac{a}{4}-\\frac{b}{2}+1)^{2} $ &nbsp;= ................</p>\n', '<p>$ (&nbsp;&nbsp;\\frac{a}{4}-\\frac{b}{2}+1)^{2} $ = &nbsp;$ (&nbsp;\\frac{a}{4})^{2} $ &nbsp;+&nbsp;$ (&nbsp;\\frac{-b}{2})^{2} $ + &nbsp;$ 1^{2} + $ + 2&nbsp;$ (&nbsp;\\frac{a}{4})&nbsp;$&nbsp;$ (&nbsp;\\frac{-b}{2})&nbsp;$ + 2&nbsp;$ (&nbsp;\\frac{-b}{2})$ (1) + 2 (1)&nbsp;$ (&nbsp;\\frac{a}{4})&nbsp;$</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; = &nbsp;$ \\frac{&nbsp;a^{2} &nbsp;}{16} $ +&nbsp;$ \\frac{ b^{2}&nbsp;&nbsp;}{4} $ + 1 -&nbsp;$ &nbsp;\\frac{ab}{4}&nbsp;$ &nbsp;- &nbsp;b &nbsp;+&nbsp;$ &nbsp;\\frac{a}{2}&nbsp;$</p>\n\n<p>Ans : A</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4508, '<p>If &nbsp;a + b + c = 9 and ab + bc + ca &nbsp;= &nbsp;26 &nbsp;then &nbsp;$ a^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ b^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ c^{2} $ = .............</p>\n', '<p>a + b + c = 9</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;Squaring &nbsp;on &nbsp;both &nbsp;sides&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>$ (a + b + c&nbsp;)^{2} $ &nbsp; = &nbsp;$ 9^{2} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;$ a^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ b^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ c^{2} $ + 2ab + 2bc + 2ca &nbsp;= &nbsp;81&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;$ a^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ b^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ c^{2} $ &nbsp;= 81 - 2 (ab + bc + ca )</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 81 -2 (26)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = 81 - 52 &nbsp;= &nbsp;29</p>\n\n<p>Ans : B</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
