(4532, '<p>For &nbsp;the &nbsp;polynomial &nbsp; f&nbsp;(y) =&nbsp;$ y^{5} $ + &nbsp;4$ y^{3} $ - 5$ y^{2} $+ y - 1 , one &nbsp;of &nbsp;the factors &nbsp;is ............</p>\n', '<p>f&nbsp;(y) = &nbsp;$ y^{5} $ + &nbsp;4$ y^{3} $ - 5$ y^{2} $+ y - 1</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;By &nbsp;trials &nbsp;f&nbsp;(1) &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ (1)^{5} $ + &nbsp;4$ (1)^{3} $ - 5$ (1)^{2} $+ (1)&nbsp;- 1</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;1 &nbsp;+ &nbsp;4 &nbsp;- 5 &nbsp;= &nbsp; 5 - 5 &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; ( y&nbsp;- 1) is &nbsp;one of &nbsp;the &nbsp;factor&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Ans : B</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
