(4553, '<p>The &nbsp;value &nbsp;of &nbsp;&#39;k&#39; &nbsp;in &nbsp;the &nbsp;expression &nbsp;4$ y^{3} $ - 7$ y^{2} $ + 6y - 3k , if &nbsp;it &nbsp;exactly divisible &nbsp;by &nbsp;y + 2 &nbsp;is&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>f (y) &nbsp;= &nbsp;4$ y^{3} $ - 7$ y^{2} $ + 6y - 3k</p>\n\n<p>f (-2) &nbsp;= 0</p>\n\n<p>4$ (-2)^{3} $ - 7$ (-2)^{2} $ + 6(-2)&nbsp;- 3k &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;4 (8) - &nbsp;28 &nbsp;- 12 - 3k &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; - 72 - 3k &nbsp;= 0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;3k &nbsp;= &nbsp;72</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;k &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{- 72}{3} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; k &nbsp;= &nbsp;- 24</p>\n\n<p>Ans : B</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4554, '<p>The &nbsp;value &nbsp;a + b + c is ........... if&nbsp;$ a^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ b^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ c^{2} $ = 18 &nbsp;and &nbsp;ab + bc + ca &nbsp;= - 9</p>\n', '<p>&nbsp; $ (a + b + c)^{2} $&nbsp; =&nbsp; &nbsp;$ a^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ b^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ c^{2} $ &nbsp;+ &nbsp;2ab + &nbsp;2bc &nbsp;+ &nbsp;2ca</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;$ a^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ b^{2} $ +&nbsp;$ c^{2} $ + &nbsp;2&nbsp;(ab + bc + ca)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;18 &nbsp;+ &nbsp;2 ( -9)&nbsp; &nbsp;= 18 &nbsp;- &nbsp;18 &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;$ (a + b + c)^{2} $ &nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;(a + b + c)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>Ans : A</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
