(4749, '<p>A &nbsp;car &nbsp;starts &nbsp;from &nbsp;rest &nbsp;and &nbsp;attains &nbsp;constant &nbsp;speed &nbsp;of &nbsp; 20 m$ s^{-1} $ in &nbsp;4s. &nbsp;Its &nbsp;acceleration &nbsp;is ..............&nbsp;m$ s^{-2} $. &nbsp;[ Car &nbsp;moves &nbsp;in &nbsp;straight &nbsp;line ]</p>\n', '<p>Acceleration &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{&nbsp;\\bigtriangleup &nbsp;V&nbsp;}{t} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{ v &nbsp;- &nbsp;u&nbsp;}{t} $</p>\n\n<p>Where &nbsp;u &nbsp;= &nbsp;initial &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;or &nbsp;speed [ 0 &nbsp;m$ s^{-1} $ ]</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;v &nbsp;= &nbsp;final &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;or &nbsp;speed &nbsp;[ 20 &nbsp;m$ s^{-1} $ ]</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;t &nbsp;= &nbsp;time &nbsp;during &nbsp;which &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;changes</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;a &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{v - u}{t} $ &nbsp; put &nbsp;the &nbsp;given &nbsp;n &nbsp;values</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{20m&nbsp;s^{-1} &nbsp;- &nbsp;0&nbsp;m&nbsp;s^{-1} }{4 s} $ &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp; 5 &nbsp;m$ s^{-2} $</p>\n\n<p>Remember</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;1 . Whenever &nbsp;body &nbsp;starts &nbsp;from &nbsp;rest, &nbsp;u &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;2 . Whenever &nbsp;a &nbsp;moving &nbsp;body &nbsp;comes &nbsp;to &nbsp;rest &nbsp;v &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
