(4759, '<p>The &nbsp;following &nbsp;s - t &nbsp;graph &nbsp;represents</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/84.png" style="height:240px; width:300px" /></p>\n', '<p>Initially &nbsp;body &nbsp;in &nbsp;covering &nbsp;less &nbsp;distance &nbsp;per &nbsp;unit &nbsp;time &nbsp;i.e &nbsp;less &nbsp;velocity. &nbsp;Later &nbsp;it &nbsp;is &nbsp;covering &nbsp;more &nbsp;distance &nbsp;per &nbsp;unit &nbsp;time i.e more &nbsp;velocity.</p>\n\n<p>Acceleration &nbsp;and &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;both &nbsp;are &nbsp;variable.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Body &nbsp;is &nbsp;moving &nbsp;with &nbsp;increasing &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;and &nbsp;acceleration.</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
