(4763, '<p>From &nbsp;the &nbsp;graph , &nbsp;displacement &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;body &nbsp;after &nbsp;10 s &nbsp;is ............m</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/86(1).png" style="height:224px; width:280px" /></p>\n', '<p>&nbsp; Displacement &nbsp;= &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;X &nbsp;time</p>\n\n<p>It &nbsp;is &nbsp;linear &nbsp;graph. &nbsp;The &nbsp;body &nbsp;is &nbsp;moving &nbsp;with &nbsp;constant &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;or &nbsp;speed.</p>\n\n<p>We &nbsp;have &nbsp;found &nbsp;v &nbsp;= &nbsp;2 m$ s^{-1} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;time &nbsp;( t ) &nbsp;= &nbsp;10 s</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;s &nbsp;= &nbsp;vt</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp; &nbsp;2 m$ s^{-1} $ &nbsp;X &nbsp;10 s</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;20 m.</p>\n\n<p>After 10 s , &nbsp;body &nbsp;was &nbsp;20 m &nbsp;away &nbsp;from &nbsp;its &nbsp;starting &nbsp;point.</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4764, '<p>From &nbsp; the &nbsp;graph &nbsp;find &nbsp;time &nbsp;taken &nbsp;to &nbsp;cover &nbsp;70 m &nbsp;is .............. sec.<img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/89.png" style="height:224px; width:280px" />s</p>\n', '<p>&nbsp; velocity &nbsp; = &nbsp;$ \\frac{&nbsp;s_{2} -&nbsp;s_{1}&nbsp;}{t_{2} - t_{1}} $</p>\n\n<p>It &nbsp;is &nbsp;linear &nbsp;graph. &nbsp;Therefore &nbsp;you &nbsp;can &nbsp;select &nbsp;any &nbsp;2 &nbsp;consucative &nbsp;values &nbsp;as &nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{1}$ &nbsp;and &nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{2}$ . &nbsp;For &nbsp;time, &nbsp;corresponding &nbsp;2 &nbsp;values have &nbsp;to &nbsp;selected &nbsp;for $ t_{1}$ &nbsp;and &nbsp;$ t_{2}$</p>\n\n<p>For &nbsp;example &nbsp;let&nbsp;&nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{1}$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;20 &nbsp;corresponding &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ t_{1}$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;10 s</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Then &nbsp; &nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{2}$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;30 &nbsp;corresponding &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ t_{2}$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;15 s</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;If &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{1}$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;10, &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{2}$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;20</p>\n\n<p>You &nbsp;may &nbsp;observe &nbsp;that &nbsp;as &nbsp;it &nbsp;is &nbsp;linear &nbsp;graph,</p>\n\n<p>$&nbsp;s_{2}$ -&nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{1}$ &nbsp; = &nbsp;constant &nbsp;[ 10 m ]</p>\n\n<p>$&nbsp;s_{2}$ -&nbsp;$&nbsp;s_{1}$ &nbsp;= &nbsp;constant &nbsp;[ 5 s ]</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; Velocity &nbsp;( v ) &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{30 -20}{15-10} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{10}{5} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;v &nbsp;= &nbsp;2 m&nbsp;$ s^{-1} $</p>\n\n<p>Thus &nbsp;velocity &nbsp;is &nbsp;constant &nbsp;as &nbsp;it &nbsp;is &nbsp;a &nbsp;linear &nbsp;graph</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; Given &nbsp;s &nbsp;= &nbsp;70 m</p>\n\n<p>We &nbsp;have &nbsp;to &nbsp;final &nbsp;time &nbsp;when &nbsp;s &nbsp;= &nbsp;70 m</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; v &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{s}{t} $ &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>t &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{s}{v} $&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; t &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{70 m}{2 m$ s^{-1} $} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp; 35 s</p>\n\n<p>Starting &nbsp; from &nbsp;rest &nbsp;at &nbsp;t &nbsp;= 0 &nbsp;, &nbsp;body &nbsp;covers &nbsp;70 m &nbsp;after &nbsp;35 &nbsp;secs.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
