(4768, '<p>From &nbsp;the &nbsp;following &nbsp; v - t graph, &nbsp;distance &nbsp;at &nbsp;time &nbsp;15 s &nbsp;is .............m</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/96.png" style="height:240px; width:300px" /></p>\n', '<p>Draw &nbsp;a &nbsp;line &nbsp;on &nbsp;x - axis &nbsp;at &nbsp;t &nbsp;= &nbsp;15 &nbsp;parallel &nbsp;to &nbsp;y - axis &nbsp;to &nbsp;get a &nbsp;rectangle &nbsp;ABCD</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/96_sol.png" style="height:240px; width:300px" /></p>\n\n<p>Such &nbsp;that &nbsp; &nbsp;AB &nbsp;= &nbsp;CD &nbsp;= 15</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AC&nbsp; = &nbsp;BD &nbsp;= 40</p>\n\n<p>We &nbsp;know &nbsp;area &nbsp;under &nbsp;v - t &nbsp; graph &nbsp;gives &nbsp;distance</p>\n\n<p>ABCD &nbsp; = &nbsp; distance &nbsp;or &nbsp;displacement</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; s &nbsp;= &nbsp; length &nbsp; X &nbsp; breadth &nbsp;of &nbsp;ABCD</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;s &nbsp; = &nbsp; l [ AC ] &nbsp; X &nbsp; l [ CD ]</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp; 40 m$ s^{-1} $ &nbsp;X &nbsp;15 s</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp; 600 &nbsp;m</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(4769, '<p>From &nbsp;the &nbsp;following &nbsp;v - t graph , &nbsp;the &nbsp;acceleration &nbsp;is .............. m$ s^{-2} $</p>\n\n<p><img alt="" src="/ckfinder/userfiles/images/97.png" style="height:216px; width:270px" /></p>\n', '<p>This &nbsp;is &nbsp;linear &nbsp;v - t graph . sloper &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;graph &nbsp;gives &nbsp;acceleration</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Acceleration &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{&nbsp;v_{2} &nbsp;- &nbsp;v_{1}&nbsp;&nbsp;}{&nbsp;t_{2} &nbsp;- &nbsp;t_{1}} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$ v_{1} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;25 &nbsp;m$ s^{-1} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;$ v_{2} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;50 &nbsp;m$ s^{-1} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;corresponding &nbsp;time &nbsp;is</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;$ t_{1} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;10 s</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;$ t_{2} $ &nbsp; = &nbsp;20 &nbsp;s</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; a &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{50 - &nbsp;25}{20 &nbsp;- &nbsp;10} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;$ \\frac{25}{10} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; a &nbsp;= &nbsp; 2 . 5 m$ s^{-2} $</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n', NULL, 0, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
