(5105, '<p>Find &nbsp;the &nbsp;co-ordinates &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;point &nbsp;which &nbsp;divides &nbsp;the &nbsp;line &nbsp;joining &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;( 1 , -2 ) &nbsp;and &nbsp;( 4&nbsp;, 7&nbsp;) &nbsp;externally &nbsp;in &nbsp;the &nbsp;ratio &nbsp;1 : 2&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>Point &nbsp;which &nbsp;divides &nbsp;the &nbsp;line &nbsp;join &nbsp;of&nbsp; &nbsp;( 1 , -2 ) &nbsp;and &nbsp;( 4&nbsp;, 7&nbsp;) &nbsp;externally &nbsp;in &nbsp;the &nbsp;ratio &nbsp;1 : 2 &nbsp;are</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp; ($ \\frac{mx_{2}-nx_{1}}{m-n} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{my_{2}-ny_{1}}{m-n} $)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;($ \\frac{1*4-2*(1)}{1-2} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{1*7-2*(-2)}{1-2} $)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;($ \\frac{4-2}{-1} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{7+4}{-1} $) &nbsp; = &nbsp;( -2&nbsp;, -11&nbsp;)</p>\n\n<p>Ans : &nbsp;B</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(5106, '<p>The &nbsp;co-ordinates &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;points &nbsp;which &nbsp;divides &nbsp;internally , &nbsp;the &nbsp;line &nbsp;joining &nbsp; A ( -2 , 1 ) &nbsp;to &nbsp;B ( 3 , 4 ) &nbsp;in &nbsp;the &nbsp;ratio &nbsp;3 : 5</p>\n', '<p>&nbsp;= &nbsp; ($ \\frac{mx_{2}+nx_{1}}{m+n} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{my_{2}+ny_{1}}{m+n} $)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;($ \\frac{3*3+5*(-2)}{3+5} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{3*(4)+5*(1)}{3+5} $)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;($ \\frac{9-10}{8} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{12+5}{8} $) &nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;($ \\frac{-1}{8} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{17}{8} $)</p>\n\n<p>Ans : &nbsp;C</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(5107, '<p>Mid &nbsp;point &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;line &nbsp;segment &nbsp;formed &nbsp;by &nbsp;joining &nbsp;( -6 , &nbsp;3 ) &nbsp;and</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;( 4&nbsp;, -9&nbsp;) ...........&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>Mid &nbsp;point &nbsp;= &nbsp;($ \\frac{x_{1}+x_{2}}{2} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{y_{1}+y_{2}}{2} $)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;($ \\frac{-6+4}{2} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{3+(-9)}{2} $)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;&nbsp;($ \\frac{-2}{2} $ , &nbsp;$ \\frac{-6}{2} $)</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;&nbsp;( -1&nbsp;, &nbsp;-3 )</p>\n\n<p>Ans &nbsp;: A</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
