(5109, '<p>Slope &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;line &nbsp;joining &nbsp;the &nbsp;points &nbsp;( -1&nbsp;, -1&nbsp;) &nbsp;and &nbsp;&nbsp;( 1&nbsp;, - 5&nbsp;) &nbsp;is ...........&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>Slope &nbsp;= &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{y_{2}-y_{1}}{x_{2}-&nbsp;x_{1}} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{-5+1}{1+1} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{-4}{2} $ &nbsp;= &nbsp;- 2</p>\n\n<p>Ans : B</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
