(5166, '<p>x &nbsp;= &nbsp;5 , &nbsp;y &nbsp;= &nbsp;- 2 &nbsp; is &nbsp;the &nbsp;solution &nbsp;of &nbsp;linear &nbsp;equation&nbsp;</p>\n', '<p>2x +&nbsp;y &nbsp;= &nbsp;9 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; , x &nbsp;= &nbsp;5 , &nbsp;y &nbsp;= &nbsp;- 2&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;2(5)&nbsp;+ (-2)&nbsp; = &nbsp;9 &nbsp;$\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;10 - 2 &nbsp;= &nbsp;9&nbsp;$\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;8&nbsp;$ \\neq $ &nbsp;9</p>\n\n<p>x + 3y &nbsp;= &nbsp;1</p>\n\n<p>5 + 3(-2)&nbsp; = &nbsp;1&nbsp;$\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;5 - 6 &nbsp;= &nbsp;1&nbsp;$\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;- 1&nbsp;$ \\neq $ &nbsp;1</p>\n\n<p>2x -&nbsp;y &nbsp;= &nbsp;12</p>\n\n<p>2(5) -&nbsp;(-2)&nbsp; = &nbsp;12&nbsp; $\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;10 +&nbsp;2 &nbsp;= &nbsp;12&nbsp;$\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;12&nbsp;= &nbsp;12</p>\n\n<p>x + 3y &nbsp;= &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>5 + 3(-2)&nbsp; = &nbsp;0&nbsp;$\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;5 - 6 &nbsp;= &nbsp;0&nbsp;$\\Rightarrow$ &nbsp;- 1&nbsp;$ \\neq $ &nbsp;0</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;x &nbsp;= &nbsp;5 , &nbsp;y &nbsp;= &nbsp;- 2 &nbsp; is &nbsp;solution &nbsp;of &nbsp;2x -&nbsp;y &nbsp;= &nbsp;12</p>\n\n<p>Ans : &nbsp;D</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
