(5187, '<p>In &nbsp;right &nbsp;$ \\bigtriangleup $ ABC , &nbsp;AB = c , &nbsp;BC = a , AC = b &nbsp;and &nbsp;CD $\\bot$ AB. &nbsp;The &nbsp;value &nbsp;of &nbsp;x &nbsp;= ...........</p>\n', '<p>Area &nbsp;of &nbsp;$ \\bigtriangleup $ ABC &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ * base * height</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ * BC * AC &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ ab &nbsp;-----------(1)</p>\n\n<p>Now &nbsp;consider &nbsp;AB &nbsp;as &nbsp;base &nbsp;then &nbsp;CD &nbsp;is &nbsp;height&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Area &nbsp;of &nbsp;$ \\bigtriangleup $ ABC &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ * AB&nbsp;* CD &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ cx&nbsp; -----------(2)</p>\n\n<p>From &nbsp;(1) &nbsp;and &nbsp;(2) &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ ab &nbsp;= &nbsp;&nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ cx</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;x &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{ab}{c} $</p>\n\n<p>Ans : &nbsp;C</p>\n', NULL, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
(5188, '<p>The &nbsp;area &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;triangle &nbsp;ADC &nbsp;is ................ sq . cm , &nbsp;EADF &nbsp;is &nbsp;rectangle.</p>\n', '<p>Given &nbsp;that &nbsp;EADF &nbsp;is &nbsp;a &nbsp;rectangle.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;BE &nbsp;= &nbsp;6 cms , &nbsp;FB &nbsp;= &nbsp;2 &nbsp;cms</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;EA &nbsp;= &nbsp;22&nbsp;cms , &nbsp;Fc&nbsp; = &nbsp;16&nbsp; cms</p>\n\n<p>Then &nbsp;AD &nbsp;= &nbsp;FB + BE &nbsp;= &nbsp;2 + 6 &nbsp;= &nbsp;8 cms</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CD &nbsp;= &nbsp; FD - FC&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; = &nbsp;22 - 16</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CD &nbsp;= &nbsp;6 cms</p>\n\n<p>Area &nbsp;of &nbsp;the &nbsp;triangle &nbsp; ADC &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ * CD * AD</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;$ \\frac{1}{2} $ * 6 * 8</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;= &nbsp;24 &nbsp;sq . cm</p>\n\n<p>Ans : &nbsp;A</p>\n', NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, 'N', 8),
